 Review comment:
   Partition support is only available with the new physical query plan and not with the direct execution from the logical plan (which will be deprecated once the physical query execution is a little farther along - see https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-5227 for more info).
   
   Try this instead though:
   
   ```
       let plan = ctx.create_logical_plan(&sql).unwrap();
       let plan = ctx.optimize(&plan).unwrap();
       let plan = ctx.create_physical_plan(&plan, DEFAULT_BATCH_SIZE).unwrap();
       let results = ctx.collect(plan.as_ref()).unwrap();
       for batch in results {
           println!("{} x {}", batch.num_rows(), batch.num_columns());
       }
   ```

