{code:java}
df = pd.DataFrame([[np.nan]], columns=['a'])
df.to_parquet('out.parquet')
{code}

OK, I found the issue, I think.

In datafusion/src/datasource/parquet.rs, change line 247 from:
{code:java}
 for i in 0..def_levels.len() {{code}
to:
{code:java}
for i in 0..levels_read { {code}
and the test passes
